"title": "5783: agreement",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5783: agreement",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Being of one mind with others, whether for good or evil purposes. Agreement among believers is commended as a means of enhancing unity and peace, and building up the people of God.</p>\n<h2>Agreements made by deliberate choice</h2>\n<h3>Agreement to do good</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:11\">JOB 2:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh5:9-Neh5:13\">NEH 5:9–5:13</a></p>\n<h3>Agreement to do wrong</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:7\">DAN 6:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:18\">JER 7:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:5-Luke22:6\">LUK 22:5–22:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:11\">MRK 14:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:1-Acts5:2\">ACT 5:1–5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:20-Acts23:21\">ACT 23:20–23:21</a></p>\n<h2>Legal agreements</h2>\n<h3>Between witnesses</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut17:6\">DEU 17:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:30\">NUM 35:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:15\">DEU 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth4:9-Ruth4:11\">RUT 4:9–4:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:16\">MAT 18:16</a></p>\n<h3>Treaties</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:19-1Kgs15:20\">1KI 15:19–15:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:3-2Chr16:4\">2CH 16:3–16:4</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:27\">GEN 21:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:28-Gen26:31\">GEN 26:28–26:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:15\">JOS 9:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh11:19\">JOS 11:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:12\">1KI 5:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:34\">1KI 20:34</a></p>\n<h2>Ways of making agreements</h2>\n<h3>By accepting terms offered</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:16\">GEN 23:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:31-Gen30:34\">GEN 30:31–30:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:24\">GEN 34:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:21\">JOS 2:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:12-Judg15:13\">JDG 15:12–15:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg17:10-Judg17:11\">JDG 17:10–17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:16-1Sam20:17\">1SA 20:16–20:17</a></p>\n<h3>Through mutually acceptable terms</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:26-Gen37:27\">GEN 37:26–37:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen13:8-Gen13:9\">GEN 13:8–13:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:19-Gen26:22\">GEN 26:19–26:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:28-Acts15:29\">ACT 15:28–15:29</a></p>\n<h3>Agreement reached by persuasion</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:12-Dan1:14\">DAN 1:12–1:14</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Agreement commended to believers</h2>\n<h3>Agreement enhances unity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr30:12\">2CH 30:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps133:1\">PSA 133:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21-John17:23\">JHN 17:21–17:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:5\">ROM 15:5</a></p>\n<h3>Agreement avoids division</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:10\">1CO 1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:16\">ROM 12:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:1-Phil2:3\">PHP 2:1–2:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:2\">PHP 4:2</a></p>\n<h2>Agreements made before God</h2>\n<h3>Agreement in prayer</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:19\">MAT 18:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs1:36\">1KI 1:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:14\">ACT 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:24\">ACT 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">ACT 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:30-Rom15:31\">ROM 15:30–15:31</a></p>\n<h3>Agreement in praise</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:6\">NEH 8:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr16:36\">1CH 16:36</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:48\">PSA 106:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:13\">PSA 41:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:19\">PSA 72:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor14:16\">1CO 14:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:13-Rev5:14\">REV 5:13–5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Agreement with God's terms</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod24:3\">EXO 24:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:22\">NUM 5:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:15-Deut27:26\">DEU 27:15–27:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:3\">2KI 23:3</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr34:32\">2CH 34:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:1-Jer11:5\">JER 11:1–11:5</a></p>",
